VIVSUALIZING TREE = RECURSION TREE


main       ^
 |         |
print(1)   ^
 |         |
print(2)   ^
 |         |
print(3)  _|

QUE - HOW TO KNOW WHEN TO USE RECURSION?
ANS - TRY TO BREAK THE QUESTION INTO SMALLER PARTS

----------------------------------
| fibo(n) = fibo(n-1) + fibo(n-2) | -> this is called recursion relation
----------------------------------
RECURIOUS RELATION = WHEN WE BREAK THE RECURSION IN FORMULAE

